entry.title: Kichler - 18'' LED Hardscape Light w/ Mounting Bracket 2700K (Textured Black) - 16103BKT27
entry.summary:
Vendor: Kichler
Type: Hardscape
Price: 179.99

Kichler LED hardscape lights are the perfect solution for outdoor applications such as lighting stairs, concrete walls, and benches. This fixture is intended to be installed between brick or masonry as youre building and wired to a magnetic landscape transformer.

The 12V LED Hardscape light is an integrated, fully sealed LED fixture with a 270° pivot rotation from a mounting bracket which allows you to place the light precisely where it's needed. The 18" length option fits most design applications with a 2700K color temperature in a Textured Black (BKT) finish. Custom optics ensure smooth, uniform light distribution virtually eliminating any hotspots or glare. Integrated with a 4kV surge protection to defend against power surges and irregularities.

entry.title: Kichler - 12V 12W Adjustable Lumen VLO LED Large Accent Light - 2700K - 15 Degree Flood Beam (Textured Black) - 16018BKT27
entry.summary:
Vendor: Kichler
Type: Accent Lights
Price: 214.99

12V with Variable Lumen Output (VLO) that allows you to easily switch between three lumen outputs (100, 200, 300 lumens) without mechanically adjusting the settings on the fixture. The adjustable lumen large accent 15 degree wide flood, 2700K spot light in textured black (BKT) is an integrated, fully sealed LED fixture that features 6,000 volt surge protection. Featuring custom optics that assures no halos or scallops to deliver superb center-to-edge uniformity for clean, clear light.

Features

  • Delivers three different lumen outputs that can be changed on site with a magnetic key without the increased risk of failure with mechanical adjustment
  • Adjusting Lumen Output
    • Simply hold the magnetic key over the lumen adjustment locator and the light will blink 4 times indicating that it is programmable
    • Reapply the magnetic key over the switch locator and the light will blink according to its lumen level (1, 2 or 3 blinks)
  • 6,000 volt surge protection
  • Crafted from aluminum and brass
  • Includes a clear glass shade
  • Integrated LED lighting
  • This product is designed for use outdoors
  • Made in Taiwan
  • ETL rated for wet locations

Dimensions

  • Height: 3-3/4"
  • Width: 4-1/2"
  • Depth: 2"
  • Product Weight: 1.5 lbs
  • Beam Spread: 15°

Electrical Specifications

  • Bulb Base: Integrated LED
  • Bulb Included: Yes
  • Wattage: 12 watts
  • Voltage: 12 volts
  • Color Temperature: 2700K
  • Color Rendering Index: 80CRI
  • Average Hours: 50000
